North Korea declares that disarmament cannot in any case be unilaterally without trust.
On Saturday, the North Korean Foreign Minister told the United Nations that maintaining sanctions increased his distrust of the United States and that it would be impossible for his country to unilaterally give up its nuclear weapons under these circumstances.
